			<td colspan="6" class="DetailTitle" style="text-align:center;">
                            Summary on Grant Application Form</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="6" class="DetailValue" style="padding:5px;">
                        <span id="lblAbstract">We propose to investigate the formation of large single colloidal crystals in a model hard-sphere colloid, sterically stabilised PMMA, by imposing a variety of external fields: shear, temperature gradient and electric field.  Structure formation will be probed by light scattering and direct observation in an optical microscope.  Both monodisperse colloids and binary mixtures will be studied.</span>
                        </td>
		</tr>
